<item>
            <title>[KNOX-849] Fix SimplePrincipalMapper and CommonIdentityAssertionFilter</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KNOX-849</link>
                <project id="12314427" key="KNOX">Apache Knox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;AbstractIdentityAssertionFilter provides the use of SimplePrincipalMapper so that others can provide the same principal mapping capabilities as Default/Simple. However, CommonIdentityAssertionFilter which is derived from it hides its availability and therefore it isn&apos;t used by any of the other providers.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Need to fix this and make sure that the same principal mapping capabilities and configuration is available across all identity assertion providers.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13034946">KNOX-849</key>
