                            <comment id="15990080" author="lmccay" created="Sun, 30 Apr 2017 00:56:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve refactored the use of the SimplePrincipalMapper from out of the DefaultIdentityAsserter filter into the CommonIdentityAssertionFilter. This allows the based principal mapping to be used with all extensions of the CIAF base and the use of the principal mapping elements.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve tested it with existing CIAF derivatives and it works well.&lt;br/&gt;
The principal mapping will be executed before the extension specific logic as to incorporate that mapping in any additional rules.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
